126
00:12:18,530 --> 00:12:21,408
[ Sighs ]
Well-

127
00:12:21,533 --> 00:12:24,036
Billy, you want me
to, um-

128
00:12:24,161 --> 00:12:26,079
No.

129
00:12:32,044 --> 00:12:34,087
Hello. Jane!

130
00:12:34,213 --> 00:12:38,217
Where are you?
You're downstairs?

131
00:12:38,342 --> 00:12:40,928
No! Just stay there,
all right?

132
00:12:41,011 --> 00:12:42,930
just stay where you're at.
I'm on my way down.

133
00:12:43,013 --> 00:12:45,224
[ Hangs Up Phone ] What do
you want me to tell 'em, Billy?

134
